#### Add new key

```bash
gnokey add wallet_name
```

#### Recover existing key

```bash
gnokey add wallet_name --recover
```

#### List all keys

```bash
gnokey list
```

#### Delete key

```bash
gnokey delete wallet_name
```

### Check balance

```bash
gnokey query -remote "https://rpc.test7.testnets.gno.land:443" auth/accounts/$ADDRESS
```